{
  "stem": "17001.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Little did we know now that the place Kistarcsa where they wanted to deport us, they were a terrible concentration place, where from there, they were taking the people to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that time, we weren't aware of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened is that we know somebody who was very good friends with this mayor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we gave some money and the questionnaire disappeared, the paper disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything disappeared, and we were left in peace.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were times when they took away the-- the permit from every Jew, because they felt that the Jew is not entitled to have a permit.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you were a businessman, any kind of businessman, they took the permit away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called in all the young men for the working battalion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took away the permit to make a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Meantime, the whole population was put on ration.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Soap you couldn't get.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Flour and fat, you know, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So meantime-- and the fat part didn't affected us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we were raising all kinds of domestic animals, like goose, the ducks, and chickens, so we had the egg supply.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had the potatoes from the garden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had the corn and we had all the fruit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother would preserve the fruit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She would make-- preserve the pickles and cabbage and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when it came to food, we were pretty well taken care of from our land, what we had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you still needed soap and you still needed clothing to wear, and is not that easy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When-- when your hand is tired, you can't move it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But with money, you were able to get it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You were able to get around with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
